OL,3,CGeorge Galloway promises to give
OL,4,CLabour and Tories 'good kicking'
OL,6,FWatch George Galloway's first speech
OL,7,Fsince taking his seat in the Commons
OL,8,Fas Rochdale's MP.
OL,10,FThe new Rochdale MP has hit out at
OL,11,FLabour and the Conservative party -
OL,12,Fclaiming most people "feel a wish for
OL,13,Fa plague on both their houses".
OL,15,FThe leader of the Workers Party of
OL,16,FBritain criticised the Chancellor's
OL,17,FBudget was an "absolute nothing
OL,18,Fburger" which would not help the town
OL,19,Fhe now represents.
