OL,6,FAn MP's first speech is usually known
OL,7,Fas their maiden speech, but Mr
OL,8,FGalloway has previously represented
OL,9,Fseats in Glasgow, east London and
OL,10,FBradford in the Commons, for Labour
OL,11,Fand later the Respect Party.
OL,13,FThe newly elected MP swept to victory
OL,14,Fin Greater Manchester seat Rochdale,
OL,15,Fgaining almost 40% of the vote.
OL,17,FHe described his Rochdale predecessor
OL,18,FSir Tony as a "significant figure"
OL,19,Fthat should never be forgotten in the
OL,20,FHouse.
