OL,4,CLabour and Tories 'good kicking'
OL,6,FMr Galloway went on to criticise
OL,7,FLabour, telling MPs that the party was
OL,8,F"not the party today that it was back
OL,9,Fthen"
OL,11,FHe said: "...in this speech and later
OL,12,Fspeeches I hope ` if God spares me and
OL,13,Fyou (Madame Deputy Speaker) allow me
OL,14,Fto catch your eye ` but Tony Lloyd
OL,15,Fnotwithstanding the very poor odour in
OL,16,Fwhich the Labour Party is held in the
OL,17,Ftown of Rochdale, the only thing that
OL,18,Funites the entire town of Rochdale is
OL,19,Fantipathy towards the Labour council
OL,20,Fin the beautiful, new, refurbished
OL,21,Ftown hall."
