OL,3,CGeorge Galloway promises to give
OL,4,CLabour and Tories 'good kicking'
OL,6,F"That is something we intend to change
OL,7,Fin just a few weeks from now at the
OL,8,Flocal elections," he added.
OL,10,FMr Galloway went on to criticise the
OL,11,Flack of public services in Rochdale,
OL,12,Finsisting it was not possible to
OL,13,Feither be born or die in the town due
OL,14,Fto lack of hospital facilities.
OL,16,FHe claimed Rochdale had become a
OL,17,F"subdivision of Oldham" because its
OL,18,Fpostcode begins with OL.
