OL,6,FMr Galloway said he had "garnered more
OL,7,Fvotes" than all of the main parties
OL,8,F"put together" in the Rochdale by-
OL,9,Felection, adding: "Proving my point
OL,10,Fthat actually outside in the country
OL,11,Fmost people feel a wish for a plague
OL,12,Fon both of their houses.
OL,14,F"Two cheeks of the same backside is
OL,15,Fthe most popular phrase I have ever
OL,16,Fcoined, because it so aptly describes
OL,17,Fnot just the general political
OL,18,Fsituation, but the debate on this very
OL,19,FBudget itself."
